oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Seldom Scene Live at the Cellar Door
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Seldom Scene's (musical group) performance at the Cellar Door. The tape also features tracks by Bluegrass (musical group), Willie Nelson (musician) and the Rice Brothers (musical group). The date of the recording is unidentified.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Seldom Scene; Bluegrass; Willie Nelson; Rice Brothers
